high_descs: Walk forward to the corner of the counter.
Pick up a knife from the counter.
Turn to the tomato on the top shelf.
Slice the tomato on the shelf.
Move the slices of tomato on the shelf apart from each other with the knife.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the shelf.
Turn around and bring the tomato slice to the sink.
Rinse the tomato in the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room.
Put the tomato slice in the trash can on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed slice of tomato in a trash can.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room and face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look up to face the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn to the right and face the right side of the sink.
Rinse the tomato slice in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To clean a slice of tomato and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Go to the counter on the right of the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Move up to the upper counter
Slice the tomato on the upper counter
Split the sliced tomato in half.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Go to the sink on the right.
Wash the slice of tomato in the sink under water.
Take the washed tomato to the trash can on the floor
Place the tomato in the trash can next to the cleaner bottle.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a washed slice of tomato.
